<section>
    <h2>About</h2>
    <p>Dillon is a lightweight application that allows users to raise events (such as keypresses and joystick movement) on a host machine by interacting with themed graphical user interfaces displayed on different devices.</p>
    <iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/GhvTY0fr9bM" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>
